 After being Africa's last hope of a place in the last 16, Colombia secured a 1-0 victory against Senegal in their Soccer World Cup Group H clash at the Samara Arena in Russia. Even though Senegal and Japan had the same goal difference (goals scored and goals conceded), Japan advances over Senegal on a 'Fair Play' tie-breaker: Senegal has 6 yellow cards, while Japan only has 4 yellow cards.  